《'''游客'''》 ({{lang-sv|'''Turist'''}}) 是一部2014年[[鲁本·奥斯特伦德|鲁本·奥斯特伦德]]编剧并执导的瑞典剧情片。赢得[[第67届坎城影展|第67届坎城影展]][[一種注目|一種注目]]单元之评审团奖<ref name="Cannes2014">{{cite web |url=http://www.festival-cannes.fr/en/article/60533.html |title=2014 Official Selection |accessdate=18 April 2014 |work=Cannes |archive-date=2016-03-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160329203309/http://www.festival-cannes.fr/en/article/60533.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.festival-cannes.com/en/theDailyArticle/61130.html |title=Un Certain Regard 2014 Awards |accessdate=23 May 2014 |work=Festival de Cannes 2014 |archive-date=2014-05-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140524004153/http://www.festival-cannes.com/en/theDailyArticle/61130.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，并选入[[多伦多影展|多伦多影展]]特别展映单元<ref name="Indiewire">{{cite web |url=http://variety.com/2014/film/news/tiff-toronto-intl-film-festival-gala-special-presentations-1201266480/ |title=Toronto Film Festival Lineup |accessdate=22 July 2014 |work=Variety |archive-date=2015-04-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150421232954/http://variety.com/2014/film/news/tiff-toronto-intl-film-festival-gala-special-presentations-1201266480/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。代表瑞典角逐[[第87屆奧斯卡金像獎|第87届奥斯卡]][[奥斯卡最佳外语片|最佳外语片]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.sfi.se/en-GB/Press/Press-archive/Force-Majeure--Swedens-2014-entry-for-the-Oscars/ |title=Force Majeure – Sweden's 2014 entry for the Oscars |accessdate=1 September 2014 |work=Swedish Film Institute Press Release |archive-date=2015-01-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150104233517/http://www.sfi.se/en-GB/Press/Press-archive/Force-Majeure--Swedens-2014-entry-for-the-Oscars/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 剧情 ==
一个瑞典家庭在[[阿尔卑斯山|阿尔卑斯山]]滑雪胜地[[旅游|旅游]]，他们就餐时遇到了[[雪崩|雪崩]]，因丈夫托马斯只顾自己逃命不救妻儿引发了家庭危机。

